      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Dancing Parasol, Snowy Breeze",
        "Client": "Guild Master Hojo",
        "Description": "Ah, \u003CPL\u003E!\r\nMinoto asked me to make some\r\nCohoot stickers and, johoho, they\r\ncame out better than expected!\r\nWouldn\u0027t you agree? Complete\r\nmy request, and they\u0027re yours!\r\nNow...hop to it-to it!",
